{
  "stem": "14190.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It's sort of-- you would call it probably kindergarten, so nurseries.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The kids were all different ages in that children's center.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There were two ladies, Jewish ladies, that were sort of taking care of us, babysitting or teaching us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was not very much of teaching going on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Although, we did sing some songs there until our parents came from work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The parents, they were going out of the ghetto to work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then, usually, in the evening, they would come to pick us up and to go-- go take us home.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother was a seamstress and working.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I remember the place because she kept talking about it, [NON-ENGLISH], whatever that is.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] Some kind of a factory that-- with the abbreviation of [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What was it?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that was-- that was the place that she worked.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father, I think, dug ditches.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know exactly what he was doing, but he was working also.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they both came approximately at the same time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, there was one incident that I remember that precipitated the fact that we had to leave ghetto, is that, one day, that when we were in children's home, several buses came.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It looks like-- it looked a little bit like the school buses over here except the color was different.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was like a brownish-- a brown color.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the windows were-- the window were taped with like a cardboard or something.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And several of the buses came near the children's center.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I saw-- I saw several German officers came and talked to the two ladies that were with us in the-- I can't tell you how many children were there.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "A lot of kids.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "More than a hundred.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
